FOLDER.NAME: DMW_INTG_DEV
FOLDER.DESCRIPTION: integration development folder for DMW project.

MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: This mapping is polling the values corresponding to unprocessed study IDs.
MAPPING.NAME: m_STG_IXH_SERVER_FILE_TRANSFER

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT V_POL.DMW_UPSTREAM_JOB_POLLING_ID, V_POL.EXECUTION_STATUS, V_POL.LIFECYCLE, V_POL.DATAMODEL, V_POL.SOURCE_NAME, V_POL.CREATED_DATETIME, V_POL.INPUT_FILE_NAME, V_POL.INPUT_FILE_PATH, V_POL.OUTPUT_FILE_NAME, V_POL.LOAD_STATUS, V_POL.STUDY_ID, V_POL.JOB_NAME, V_POL.DMW_UPSTREAM_FILE_ID, V_POL.STUDY_INT_JOB_ID, V_POL.RUN_TYPE, V_POL.DATA_PULL_TYPE from $$SRC_SCHEMA.$$SRC_VIEW V_POL where V_POL.EXECUTION_STATUS='0' AND V_POL.JOB_NAME = '$$JOB_NAME' AND V_POL.DMW_UPSTREAM_JOB_POLLING_ID <= (select distinct min(DMW_UPSTREAM_JOB_POLLING_ID) from $$SRC_SCHEMA.$$SRC_VIEW where JOB_NAME = '$$JOB_NAME' AND EXECUTION_STATUS='0')

MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: Mapping is updating the status in SDLU database.
MAPPING.NAME: m_FILE_TRANSFER_STATUS_UPDATE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT VPOL.DMW_UPSTREAM_JOB_POLLING_ID, VPOL.EXECUTION_STATUS, VPOL.LIFECYCLE, VPOL.DATAMODEL, VPOL.SOURCE_NAME, VPOL.CREATED_DATETIME, VPOL.INPUT_FILE_NAME, VPOL.INPUT_FILE_PATH, VPOL.OUTPUT_FILE_NAME, VPOL.LOAD_STATUS, VPOL.STUDY_ID, VPOL.JOB_NAME, DUF.DMW_UPSTREAM_FILE_ID, SIJ.STUDY_INT_JOB_ID FROM $$SRC_SCHEMA.$$SRC_VIEW VPOL, $$SRC_SCHEMA.$$UPSTREAM_FILES_TABLE DUF, $$SRC_SCHEMA.$$STUDY_INT_TABLE SIJ WHERE VPOL.DMW_UPSTREAM_JOB_POLLING_ID = DUF.DMW_UPSTREAM_JOB_POLLING_ID AND SIJ.STUDY_INT_JOB_ID = VPOL.STUDY_INT_JOB_ID AND VPOL.STUDY_ID = $$STUDY_ID AND VPOL.DMW_UPSTREAM_JOB_POLLING_ID = $$DMW_UPSTREAM_JOB_POLLING_ID

Message : Polling session %s failed while fetching the last unprocessed records.
Below are the components used in session:
Session Name :- %s 
 Repository Name :- %d 
 Session Status :- %e
 Mapping name :- %m 
 Folder Name :- %n

 Session Completion Time :- %c
